\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5899499 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9991975\charrsid13268011 Oh, 
a friend from Talsarnau. My mother didn't know that we - that I went and when I came home - you see, they'd been tarring the road and I had a new cotton frock on, it was pink, and the bike had splashed coal tar all over it. And then a man came on a horse 
about two weeks later and he said, I saw Jeannie in Beddgelert, and that was the first my mother heard of the fact that I'd been away on the bike. I mean, she'd seen the frock before.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202737 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9991975\charrsid13268011 What happened?
