\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5899499 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9991975\charrsid13268011 No. No. Remember he was a preacher, I never saw even the smallest bottle of brandy there. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202737 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9991975\charrsid13268011 Did they ever make any medicine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5899499 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9991975\charrsid13268011 No.
